{"word":"G2605 - καταγγέλλω - katangéllō - kat-ang-gel'-lo - Declare","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καταγγέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">katangéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kat-ang-gel'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Declare</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரசங்கி, அறிவி, போதி, சொல், தெரிவி"},{"paragraph":"to announce, to declare, to promulgate, to make known; to proclaim publicly, to publish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2596 - κατά - katá - kat-ah'/2596\">G2596</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G32 - ἄγγελος - ángelos - ang'-el-os/32\">G32</a>; to <i>proclaim</i>, <i>promulgate:</i> - declare, preach, shew, speak of, teach.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1229/1229\">G1229</a>, <a href=\"#/G1804/1804\">G1804</a>, <a href=\"#/G2604/2604\">G2604</a>, <a href=\"#/G2605/2605\">G2605</a>, <a href=\"#/G31/31\">G31</a>, <a href=\"#/G312/312\">G312</a>, <a href=\"#/G4293/4293\">G4293</a>, <a href=\"#/G518/518\">G518</a>"}]}